CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of women and men, including Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence standing behind banquet table in center, and Eunice Cook wearing light colored suit and hat with wide brim, seated second from right, in gymnasium set with banquet table with light colored floral tablecloth and floral arrangements
